Steps - 

1. Creating a project -
	Create a project 'CRUD' folder inside XAMPP/htdocs
	Create index.php

2. Creating the DB -
	Create database  Demo in localhost/phpmyadmin
	Create a table 'crud' inside Demo DB manually

3. Connecting to the DB - 
	Create connect.php
	Include connect.php inside index.php

4. Insert data into table, index.php.

5. Retrieve and show the data in view.php
